# Change Log

## 2026-04-24

- Added nginx handling for `/confs/*.conf` in `staff/nginx.conf`, serving files from `/var/www/demo-cms/confs/`.
- Documented the `/confs/*.conf` nginx behavior in `README.md`.

## 2026-04-25

- CMS bootstrap: when `ADMINS` is empty and `cms_users` is empty, `/cms/login` shows first-admin form; POST writes `ADMINS` to `.env` (argon2 hash), clears `get_settings` cache, sets session `bootstrap_pending_restart`, shows restart instructions (`app/routers/cms.py`, `app/env_bootstrap.py`, templates `cms/bootstrap_*.html.j2`).
- Added `repo.count_cms_users` for bootstrap detection.
- README: documented first run without `ADMINS`.
- Translated `README.md` and all Jinja2 CMS/article templates to English; aligned login/bootstrap error strings in `app/routers/cms.py`.

## 2026-04-26

- Added `Settings.debug` / env `DEBUG`; when true, `DebugRequestLoggingMiddleware` in `app/debug_request_logging.py` logs HTTP request/response headers and truncated bodies to stdout; wired in `app/main.py` after `SessionMiddleware`. Documented in `README.md` and `.env.example`.
- Verstka: strip `VERSTKA_API_KEY` / `VERSTKA_API_SECRET` / `VERSTKA_CALLBACK_URL` on load; pass `debug=settings.debug` into `VerstkaConfig` for richer callback signature errors. README: `invalid_signature` troubleshooting.
